{"tid":1459922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"816 816 加速支爆行動! (和你飛再升級)","createTime":"2019-08-12T23:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:29:56.000Z","uid":222190,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"4a721bc9885669e632699f16b13a0e46c71ec63f","tid":1459922,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:50:45.000Z","msg":"和你飛行動非常成功，<span style=\"color: gold;\">但如果想加速經濟壓力支爆，我們還有一招可以出</span>：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cLMUcg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cLMUcg.png&h=cbdda782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">816，下星期五，請將所有銀行存款從銀行中提走，記住是提走或匯到離岸戶口，而非從一間銀行轉到另一間銀行，並將MPF組合全部轉成非香港及中國資產。</span><br />\n<br />\n一眾手足在前線浴血奮戰，我們沒有能力上前線的，至少要利用自己鈔票的力量，表明我們對現任政府已經失去信心。<br />\n<br />\n香港銀行體系結餘只有五百多億，如果二百萬人每人提走$25,000，已經能夠令結餘歸零。之後，就讓信用塌縮完成餘下的工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gEM4FSW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgEM4FSW.png&h=d076c59c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Black up:<br />\n【聯繫匯率】金管局：銀行體系結餘下降增拆息港匯波動<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563182627578&amp;issue=20190715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1563182627578%26issue%3D20190715&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=02af632e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1563182627578%26issue%3D20190715&h=4345b7bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1563182627578&amp;issue=20190715</a><br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】前Big Four會計師講金融抗爭 政局不穩兌美金保平安「手中鈔票亦是抗爭工具 」<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190804&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=59890731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190804%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D59890731&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=94f9477f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190804%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D59890731&h=2e9f33ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190804&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=59890731</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(學術討論)如果有2百萬人同時去銀行㩒錢 會點樣？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403878</a></span>"},{"pid":"bd6e14b3b5a1ac140b7b11cdda93f549f5969598","tid":1459922,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HgyR5j1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHgyR5j1.png&h=be824722&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0ee5ce1c542ffcac193ef6e8a18e013556aaa9e","tid":1459922,"uid":222190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pSzYLj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpSzYLj6.png&h=b5eb68e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcea3e5cbce3e925f4d03ca24c64e8d67868668f","tid":1459922,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdsrUdy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdsrUdy.png&h=c0f9e7a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8c51da036ccd26bdbcdba197942fc21cfa96540","tid":1459922,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4P9R0v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4P9R0v.png&h=14e351de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aF60YFv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaF60YFv.png&h=75510b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UQhC0TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?